data.text:
Originally released in 1995, Brothas Doobie is the second album by the Los Angeles-based Latino rap group Funkdoobiest. The album contains all the original members Son Doobie (Jason Vasquez), DJ Ralph M (Ralph Medrano), and Tomahawk Funk (Tyrone Pacheco). The latter left group after this release.

180 gram audiophile vinyl

Legendary 1995 Hip-Hop album featuring the singles “Rock On”, “Dedicated” & “XXX Funk”

TRACK LISTING:

A1. This Is It (Interlude)

A2. Rock On

A3. What the Deal

A4. Lost in Thought

A5. Dedicated

A6. Ka Sera Sera

A7. Pussy Ain't Shit

B1. XXX Funk

B2. It Ain't Going Down

B3. You're Dummin'

B4. Tomahawk Bang

B5. Superhoes

B6. Who Ra Ra
